{
  "text": "The TTO question consisted of a horizontal line, representing 0-10 years, where every year was marked and labelled 0, 1, 2, \u2026, 10 years [CITATION_1] . Every half year was marked, but not labelled. A similar TTO question has been employed in other studies [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] 43, [CITATION_4] .",
